==Drop Rate Formulas==

===GEM Drops===
<pre>
GEM_Amount = Enemy_Base_GEMs + Random(0, 2)

With Lucky Blade:
GEM_Amount = (Enemy_Base_GEMs × 1.5) + Random(0, 3)
</pre>

===Item Drops===
Rare item drop chance:
<pre>
Drop_Chance = Base_Rate + (Luck_Bonus)

Where:
  Base_Rate = 5% (standard enemies)
  Base_Rate = 10% (mini-bosses)
  Base_Rate = 100% (bosses)
  Luck_Bonus = +5% with Lucky Blade
</pre>

