==Random Number Generator==

Soul Blazer uses a 16-bit LFSR for pseudo-random values:
<pre>
Location: $7E0042 (2 bytes)
Initial seed: $0001

Update per call:
  bit = (rng ^ (rng >> 1) ^ (rng >> 3) ^ (rng >> 12)) & 1
  rng = (rng >> 1) | (bit << 15)

Returns: rng & 0xFF (low byte)
</pre>

Used for:
* Enemy behavior variations
* Drop rate calculations
* Critical hit checks
* AI decision trees

